BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION

We could begin by setting [` [$f] = [$f2]`] and solving the resulting quadratic equation for [`x`]. There is only one solution, and we can find the corresponding value of [`y`] from the equation [`y=[$f2]`].

[@ image(insertGraph($gr), width=>300, height=>300, tex_size=>700) @]***



